{"tid":581354,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"近日LOL女子隊比賽一問(Your Youth?)","createTime":"2018-03-05T09:30:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-05T16:15:25.000Z","uid":101754,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4dbeda8507e2c7f5e805d0e73a71cb3dbf572f16","tid":581354,"uid":101754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T09:30:35.000Z","msg":"是咁的, 本人唔係啲咩電莖撚, 只係係FB睇到底線出post 話<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">有好多人係圈外唔知頭唔知路, 但最可悲唔係呢班無知既人</span></span>, 咁我又唔想做無知嘅人, 所以就想問下有冇人可以講下咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我講下我知嘅野先啦, 我就知wal仔有出過post 講話<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">成班仲好似初中-小學係d論壇罵戰咁拗黎拗去，無成長過咁</span></span> 同埋講過<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">但係以前我淨係親耳聽都聽到比用腳打都贏惡毒10萬倍既說話啦</span></span><br />\n而我所知<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">用腳打都贏</span></span> 呢句係colourmc 嘅IG story 出現先嘅, 姐係啲人係因為colour 講咗呢句之後, 比其他女子隊屌?定係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申:<br />\n我係好奇想知姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時都冇留意LOL女子隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係平時J下<span style=\"color: green;\">6</span>條臭雞姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係好問一隊LOL得5條友, 何來6條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明就明, 唔明就唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">歡迎爆料</span></span>"},{"pid":"688037f922b7ac1a79ec40dd694581731f1d396c","tid":581354,"uid":34223,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T09:32:00.000Z","msg":"不如你講返人話啦"},{"pid":"822ac2427daf3f200171f07dcd6a4671d4979440","tid":581354,"uid":174,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T09:32:52.000Z","msg":"睇完成個post 都唔知你講